給 Lovable.dev 的提示詞 (Prompt)
Project Name: AI Smart Customer Service SaaS Platform (AI 智慧客服 SaaS 管理平台)
Language: Traditional Chinese (繁體中文)
Style: Modern, Professional, Clean, Tech-oriented (Suitable for a Cyber Security Studio).
Core Description:
Build a SaaS backend management dashboard for a "Line Bot AI Customer Service System". This platform allows users to manage multiple Line Bots. Each bot is linked to a specific domain of knowledge and uses RAG technology to answer customer queries. The UI must be in Traditional Chinese.
Key Design Principles:
1. SaaS Architecture: The user interface must support managing a "Pool" of Line Bots.
2. White Labeling: Do NOT use technical backend names like "AnythingLLM", "N8N", or "Vector DB" in the UI labels. Use user-friendly terms like "Knowledge Base", "Workflow Integration", "AI Brain", or "Extension Tools".
3. Completeness: Every menu item mentioned below must link to a functional page containing relevant forms, tables, or operation panels.
Page Structure & Features:
1. Dashboard (首頁儀表板)
Create a comprehensive data visualization dashboard containing:
* Key Metrics (Cards):
    * Total Token Usage (本月 Token 使用量).
    * Total Service Messages (總服務訊息數).
    * Active Users Count (活躍用戶數 - New addition).
    * Average AI Response Time (平均 AI 回應時間 - New addition).
* Charts & Lists:
    * TOP 5 Frequent Questions: A bar chart or list showing the most asked questions.
    * TOP 5 Knowledge Hits: Which documents/knowledge chunks are cited most often (labeled as "熱門引用資料").
    * Bot Status Overview: A quick status list of all managed bots (Online/Maintenance/Error).
    * Recent Alerts: A feed of system warnings or errors.
2. Navigation Sidebar (功能導覽列)
Organize the sidebar into logical groups. Ensure each item links to a specific page.
Group A: Knowledge & AI Core (智慧核心與知識庫)
* File Management (文件與知識上傳):
    * UI Label: "知識庫管理" (Knowledge Base).
    * Page Content: Drag-and-drop area for uploading PDF/TXT/Docx. A list of uploaded files with status (Processing/Embedded). Logic: This connects to the RAG vector store.
* AI Configuration (AI 參數設定):
    * UI Label: "AI 模型設定" (AI Settings).
    * Page Content: Inputs for System Prompt (系統提示詞), Temperature (創意度), and Model Selection (Dropdown).
* Agent Tools (Agent 設定):
    * UI Label: "智慧代理人設定" (Agent Settings).
    * Page Content: Toggle switches to enable specific agent capabilities (e.g., Web Browsing, Calculation).
* Extension Tools (MCP 設定):
    * UI Label: "擴充工具管理" (Extension Tools).
    * Page Content: Interface to configure external context protocols or custom tools without showing "MCP" jargon.
Group B: Integration & Automation (整合與自動化)
* Workflow Webhooks (WebHook 設定):
    * UI Label: "自動化流程串接" (Automation Workflow).
    * Page Content: Fields to input Webhook URLs for triggering external events.
* Connection Settings (API 連線設定):
    * UI Label: "模型連線配置" (Connection Config).
    * Page Content: Secure fields for API Keys, Base URLs, and Model ID selection.
Group C: Bot Management (機器人管理)
* Bot Pool (Line Bot Pool 管理):
    * UI Label: "機器人列表與狀態" (Bot Pool).
    * Page Content: A card grid or table showing all Line Bots owned by the user. Options to "Create New Bot", "Pause", or "Delete".
* Line Configuration (Line Bot 相關設定):
    * UI Label: "Line 平台串接" (Line Integration).
    * Page Content: Fields for Channel Access Token, Channel Secret, and Webhook URL generation.
* Live Chat / Human Takeover (人工回覆介入):
    * UI Label: "即時客服對話" (Live Chat).
    * Page Content: (See detailed specs below).
Group D: Administration (系統管理)
* Access Control (帳號權限管理):
    * UI Label: "成員與權限" (Team & Permissions).
    * Page Content: Invite users, assign roles (Admin, Editor, Viewer).
* User Profile: Settings for the current user and "Logout" button.
3. Notifications (訊息提示中心)
* Top Bar Icon: A bell icon showing:
    * System Warnings: (e.g., "Token quota low", "Bot disconnected").
    * Periodic Reports: (e.g., "Weekly summary available").
4. Detailed Specification for "Live Chat / Human Takeover" Page (人工回覆功能)
This page is critical for customer support. It should function like a chat application.
* Layout: Three-column layout.
    * Left (Chat List): List of active user sessions. Indicators for "AI Replying" (Green) vs "Waiting for Human" (Red). Filter options: "All", "Unread", "Human Handle".
    * Middle (Chat Window):
        * Message bubbles (Right: Agent/Human, Left: User).
        * Different visual style for AI-generated responses vs. Human-typed responses.
        * "Takeover Toggle" (介入開關): A distinct button to pause the AI for this specific user. When active, AI stops replying, and only the human agent can send messages.
        * Input area with attachment support.
    * Right (User Context & Quick Actions):
        * User Profile (Line Display Name, User ID).
        * Tags: Add tags like "VIP", "Complaint", "Sales Lead".
        * Canned Responses: Quick-click buttons for common replies.
        * Summary: A brief AI-generated summary of the conversation so far.

Gemini 幫忙做的設計補充說明：
針對您的需求，我在提示詞中特別強化了以下幾點，以符合 SaaS 商業邏輯與您的技術架構：
1. 儀表板豐富化 (Dashboard Enrichment)： 除了您提到的 Top 5 和 Token，我加入了 「活躍用戶數 (Active Users)」 和 「AI 平均回應時間」。這對於客戶來說是評估服務價值的關鍵指標。同時也加入了 「Bot Status Overview」，因為使用者有多個 Bot，一眼看到哪個 Bot 斷線或異常非常重要。
2. 隱藏技術名詞 (White Labeling)： 我將 AnythingLLM 對應的「上傳檔案」改稱為 「知識庫管理」；將 MCP 改稱為 「擴充工具管理」；將 N8N WebHook 改稱為 「自動化流程串接」。這讓您的 SaaS 看起來更像是一個獨立、專業的產品，而不是單純的工具拼裝。
3. 人工回覆規格 (Human Takeover Specs)： 這是您提到的第 5 點，我將其設計為標準的 「三欄式客服介面」。
    * 關鍵功能： 我加入了一個 "Takeover Toggle" (介入開關)。這是最重要的邏輯，當客服人員按下「接手」時，必須暫停該用戶的 AI 觸發（這通常需要後端配合旗標控制），避免人工打字時 AI 還在插嘴。
    * 右側欄位： 增加了「用戶標籤」與「對話摘要」，幫助客服快速進入狀況。
4. Bot Pool 概念： 將「Line Bot 設定」與「Pool 管理」分開。Pool 是看整體（新增/刪除 Bot），設定則是針對單一 Bot 的細項參數（Token/Secret）。
